import React, { useState } from "react"; import { useSelector } from "react-redux"; import { Button, Typography, Grid, Paper } from "@mui/material"; const Prescription = () => { const data = useSelector((state) => state.Render.Render); const currentDate = new Date().toLocaleDateString(); const [showHomeRemedy, setShowHomeRemedy] = useState(false); const handleHomeRemedy = () => { setShowHomeRemedy(!showHomeRemedy); }; const printAndDownload = () => { window.print(); // Print the prescription const prescriptionContent = document.getElementById( "prescription-content" ).innerHTML; // Get prescription content const file = new Blob([prescriptionContent], { type: "text/plain" }); // Create blob for downloading const url = URL.createObjectURL(file); const a = document.createElement("a"); a.href = url; a.download = "prescription.txt"; // Set download filename document.body.appendChild(a); a.click(); // Trigger download URL.revokeObjectURL(url); // Clean up document.body.removeChild(a); }; return (
Prescription
Name of the Patient: {data.Name} Date of Birth: {data.Dob} Age: {data.Age} Contact Number: {data.Mobile} Today's Date: {currentDate} Diagnosed with: {data.Result.CommonlyUsedforDiseases} Medication Details Ayurvedic Medicine Dosage (per day) {data.Result.MedicineName} {data.Result.Dosage} {showHomeRemedy && ( Home Remedy {data.Result.HomeRemedies} )}
); }; export default Prescription;
